These two products are a music server and fully digital amplifier, which eliminate external components, expensive and complicated wiring, and reduce distortion by eliminating audio conversion and coloration created by having more components in the signal path. Core Audio manufactures and designs each of its products from the ground up and continues to conduct R&D in house to improve technology and implementation.
